These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-7-1::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: card-games, board-games, skydiving
1. the person who's hobby is skydiving is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##5
2. the person who's hobby is skydiving is somewhere between the person who's hobby is card-games and the person who's hobby is board-games##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2   |  3   |
| Hobby   | card-games | skydiving | board-games |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-7-2::.
3 different pets are kept: fish, dog, chinchilla
1. the owner of the chinchilla is somewhere between the owner of the dog and the owner of the fish##7
2. the owner of the dog is somewhere to the right of the owner of the fish##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |   2   |   3   |
| Pet   | fish | chinchilla | dog |

 #################################

 
